<p class = 'definition' data-word = 'Translational Kinetic Energy'>
  An object has <strong>translational kinetic energy</strong>
  if its <em>center of mass</em> is moving.
</p>
<p class = 'definition' data-word = 'Rotational Kinetic Energy'>
  An object's <strong>rotational kinetic energy</strong>
  if it is <em>rotating about its center of mass</em>.
</p>

<p>
